msgctxt "332_Akiyama"
msgid "Sorry for flagging you down like that. Mind if we chat for a few?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "344_Energetic Foreigner"
msgid ""
"Of course not! I love talking to washed-up porn stars. I'm Mack: "
"photographer by trade, observer of humanity at heart! And I mean "
"<Italic>all</Italic> of humanity."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "356_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"...Right. And sorry to break it to you, but I'm actually a moneylender. I "
"run a place called Sky Finance, right over there. The name's Akiyama."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "368_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"I was hoping you'd be able to fill me in on those \"tough dudes\" you were "
"talking about before."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "380_Mack"
msgid ""
"Sure thing, slick! These scary-looking dudes were filing down the street "
"one after the other, like the world's least cheerful conga line."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "392_Mack"
msgid ""
"Wasn't sure what was happening, but I knew something mega was about to hit! "
"I was practically quaking in my sensible boots!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "404_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"Back up a second. You mentioned something about a shot, too. Do you take "
"pictures of this kinda stuff as it goes down?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "416_Mack"
msgid ""
"These aren't any old pictures, man! I've been traveling the world for what "
"feels like eons, searching for the photograph to end all photographs! The "
"<Italic>perfect shot</Italic>!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "428_Akiyama"
msgid "...Uh-huh."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "440_Mack"
msgid ""
"Look at me running my mouth like it's in a dang marathon. Akiyama-san... "
"Have you ever seen a sight so incredible, it made you realize something "
"about the nature of the world?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "452_Akiyama"
msgid "Uh, not that I can remember."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "464_Mack"
msgid ""
"Folks call those <Color:7>revelations<Color:Default>! A flash of "
"inspiration! A spark in the ol' noggin! A rush of idea juice flooding your "
"mind!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "476_Akiyama"
msgid "Yeah, that's definitely never happened to me before."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "488_Mack"
msgid ""
"Then maybe it's about time it does! And what's more, these revelations hold "
"the key to the perfect shot! I'm sure of it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "500_Akiyama"
msgid ""
"...Yeah, sure. I'll, uh, keep that in mind. Anyway, about those tough dudes "
"you mentioned..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "512_Mack"
msgid ""
"Hold up, the greatest idea just snapped across my neurons! Maybe you can "
"help me try to find the perfect shot!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "524_Akiyama"
msgid "I mean, sure, but I'd really rather just hear about－"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "536_Mack"
msgid ""
"Then it's settled! C'mon, it's huntin' time! And we're hunting the biggest "
"game of all: art!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "548_Akiyama"
msgid "(...Guess I'm just gonna have to put up with this nutjob for now.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "560_Mack"
msgid ""
"Don't look now, Akiyama-san, but I just caught a glimpse of something good! "
"Train your eyes on that roof over there!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "584_Mack"
msgid ""
"Something's up with that lady... and you're gonna snap a shot of whatever "
"it is!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "596_Mack"
msgid ""
"All you've gotta do is whip it out－your phone, I mean－and etch that moment "
"into digital divinity! Don't worry, the government probably won't see your "
"photos later."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "608_Akiyama"
msgid "...My phone camera, huh? All right, I'll see what I can do."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "620_Revelations"
msgid ""
"You can learn new techniques from <Color:7>Revelations,<Color:Default> "
"gained by witnessing particularly inspiring events around the city."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "632_Revelations"
msgid ""
"Press <Action:Button_R3@Adventure> when you see something of interest to "
"switch to <Color:7>first-person mode<Color:Default>. Use the "
"<Action:Turn_Camera_Up@Adventure><Action:Turn_Camera_"
"Down@Adventure><Action:Turn_Camera_Left@Adventure><Action:Turn_Camera_"
"Right@Adventure> to control the camera."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "644_Revelations"
msgid ""
"When \"Look\" is displayed on the top-right of the screen in "
"<Color:7>first-person mode<Color:Default>, you will have a chance to have a "
"Revelation. Look for the button icon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "656_Revelations"
msgid ""
"First Akiyama will take out his cell phone. Press the buttons displayed on "
"the screen to take a picture of the decisive moment."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "668_Revelations"
msgid ""
"If you successfully enter the correct buttons for all three pictures, you "
"will be given a multiple choice question. Select the correct answer to have "
"a Revelation and learn a new technique!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "680_Mack"
msgid ""
"Just ask me if you're shooting in the dark and I can recite all that to you "
"verbatim! Really, every word'll be exactly the same!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "692_Mack"
msgid "Akiyama-san! What's crack-a-lacking?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "704_Akiyama"
msgid "Uh, nothing right now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "716_Mack"
msgid "Gotcha! C'mon, let's give this revelation thing a whirl!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "728_Akiyama"
msgid "Do you think you could explain what revelations are again?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "740_Mack"
